data.description:
Very secluded location, end of cul de sac, lot of privacy.
Garage has special floor finish, with custom ceiling to floor cabinets, work bench. Large tool shed for storage. Shutters in lower/upper rooms.Two fireplaces.Large three car finished garage. Deck off upper master bdrm. Laundry chute from upper level to laundry/utility room on lower level. Ceiling fans in all bdrms and family room.New granite counters in kitchen. Soft water system.

Neighborhood Description

Very close to Westfield Shopping center, easy access to I-15, wonderful amenities, golf course nearby, Wild Animal Park, Lake Hodges etc.
data.whatILove: The privacy of our location at the end of a cul de sac. We are on the front edge of Lomas Serenas development, but, we are not part of, thus, no homeowner fees.
